    <criterion testable="true">`IAttachment.driveItemId` is set to `sprk_document.sprk_driveitemid` (NOT the document GUID — fixes latent bug class).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Documents with null `sprk_driveitemid` are filtered out.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Source badge displays "Related" in AttachmentList.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Xrm.WebApi used when available; BFF fallback otherwise.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`npm run build` + `npm run lint` clean.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Empirical finding: `sprk_document` GUID ≠ driveItem ID. This task hard-codes the correct resolution. Wave 5 task 075 (DocumentEmailWizard fix) is the analog for the wizard surface.

    `_sprk_parent_value` is a polymorphic / customer-specific field — adjust the actual field name based on the real Dataverse schema. The point is "filter sprk_document by parent record reference".
  </notes>

